                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-xs font-semibold rounded">Citations</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 mb-3">Best for: Academic research, fact-checking, and cited answers</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">Perplexity AI provides sources alongside every answer — making it the go-to tool for research. Every response includes clickable citations so you can verify the information instantly.</p>
              <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-3 mb-4 text-xs text-amber-800">
                <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Use Perplexity to cross-check answers from other AI chatbots. Its citation feature is unmatched in the free tier.
