              <li><strong>Best Choice:</strong> Perplexity AI or Google Gemini</li>
              <li><strong>Why:</strong> Source citations and real-time web data</li>
              <li><strong>Use Cases:</strong> Research papers, fact-checking, current events</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-5">
